es such as {JSIM} also significantly improve the reliability of {TOPCon} solar cells. This improvement is due to the compatibility of these processes with screen printing pastes that have low or zero Al concentration for the {TOPCon} front. Consequently, this approach enables using more cost-effective materials for {TOPCon} modules, thereby reducing the overall cost of solar electricity.},
